item.title: About
item.description: About Me Hello! My name is Jefferson Huynh, and I am a recent UCLA graduate who is interested in studying poltical psychology and social cognition. Broadly, my research interests revolve around the cognitive processes that influence our decision-making and attitudes/beliefs towards sociopolitical issues. Research Interests Political Psychology Social Cognition Intergroup Relations Social Networks Misinformation
